(function(skuid){
	var $ = skuid.$;
	$(document.body).one('pageload',function(){
		var modelForm = skuid.model.getModel('UserManualActionRequired');
		var modelRows = modelForm.getRows();
		
		var modelA = skuid.model.getModel('CurrentUser');
        var row = modelA.getFirstRow();
        var UID = row.Id;
        
        var modelMod = skuid.model.getModel('ModificationCount');
        var modelRw = modelMod.getFirstRow();
        var chkCount = modelRw.ReqCount;
        var count = 0;
		
		var lastupdated='';
		for(var i=0;i<modelRows.length;i++)
		{
		    var ids = modelRows[i].Id;
		    var div = document.getElementById(ids);
		    
		    var d = new Date(modelRows[i].LastModifiedDate);
            var dt = d.getDate();
            var yy = d.getFullYear();
            var mm = d.getMonth()+1;
            
            if(mm < 10)
            {
                mm = '0'+mm;
            }
            if(dt < 10)
            {
                dt = '0'+dt;
            }
            yy = yy%100; 
            
            //console.log('last updated3 '+lastupdated);
            //var profilename = modelRows[i].LastModifiedBy.Profile.Name;
            var modifiedid = modelRows[i].LastModifiedById;
           // if(profilename === 'Customer Community Login User Custom' && modifiedid != UID)
            // console.log('modifiedid '+modifiedid +' UID '+ UID );
            if(modifiedid != UID && modelRows[i].LastModifiedBy.ContactId)
            {
                lastupdated = modelRows[i].LastModifiedBy.Name+' ('+mm+'/'+dt+'/'+yy+')';    
                if(count < 1)
                {
                    count++;
                    chkCount = false;
                }
            }else
            {
                lastupdated = '';
            }
            if(div)
		    {
		       // console.log('Ids'+ids);
		        div.innerHTML  = lastupdated;
		    }else{
		        console.log('error'+ids);
		    }
            modelForm.updateRow(modelRows[i],'LastModifiedManual',lastupdated);
		}
		if(chkCount === true)
		{
		    //console.log('cn ' +chkCount);
		    modelMod.updateRow(modelRw,'ReqCount',true);
		}
		else
		{
		    //console.log('cn12 '+chkCount);
		    modelMod.updateRow(modelRw,'ReqCount',false);
		}
	});
})(skuid);
